    {"number": 1, "text": "An apparatus for processing data...", "type": "independent"},
    {"number": 2, "text": "The apparatus according to claim 1, wherein the processor is configured to...", "type": "dependent"}
]
filtered_prior_art = [
    {"document_id": "US20435678", "title": "...", "abstract": "..."}
]

claim_chart = generate_claim_chart(parsed_claims, filtered_prior_art)
print(claim_chart)
```

### Conclusion

Merging dependent claims under their respective parent independent claim provides a more comprehensive and manageable view of the patent. This approach reduces redundancy and simplifies review while maintaining clarity in FTO analysis.

